St. Raymond Avenue, north side, east from Olmstead Avenue. The three-story brick buildint is the service building of the Bronx Gas and Electric Company, at Odell Street.

Olmstead Avenue, at St. Raymond Avenue (vantage-point). The view is northeastward toward E. Tremont Avenue, across the area which will become part of the model housing development to be erected by the Metropolitan Life IIisurance Company.
